               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">2 May 1870 ¶  ¶ [Director respecting reductions in the number of employees in the gardens] ¶ The correspondence on this topic was extensive. See M toJ. McCulloch23 April 1873 (in this edition as 70-04...</supplied>
